README
======

mein editor (me) is a minimalistic ncurses-based text editor for Unix-like
operating systems.

Installation
------------
To build and install me, simply run "make" and "make install".

Build dependencies:
- ncurses (tested with 5.4)

Keys
----

Here's a list of available keys:
Down          go to next line
Up            go to previous line
PageDown      go to next page
PageUp        go to previous page
Backspace     delete character left of the cursor
DEL           delete character right of the cursor
Return        insert new line
Ctrl-A        go to begin of line
Ctrl-D        delete character right of the cursor
Ctrl-E        go to end of line
Ctrl-C        cancel editor
Ctrl-S        save file
Ctrl-W        save file as
Ctrl-X        quit editor


